          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " or Pierce Arrow or a curvaceous French coach-built mount emerges as Best of Show. Lately one might even find a 50+-year-old rare Italian two-seater showered in confetti on the concours lawn.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
